flowRoot.flowPara: We're going to build a new web page. We're going to make ours about books but you can make yours about whatever you like!

flowPara.flowSpan: Download the HTML code from http://kata.coderdojo.com/wiki/My_First_Website Go into the zip and then the
file. It opens in your web browser.

flowRoot.flowPara: Now open the same file in a plain text editor such as Notepad ++ or Sublime Text
